name: [Vortex] Hatchet
background: This inverter W-Engine can generate excessive power and effectively increase its operator's battle prowess. However, due to its poor heat dissipation, it emits ear-splitting noise during battle. As a result, all squad members will need to wear earplugs.
skill: Upon entering combat or switching in, the equipper's Impact increases by 9%/10%/11%/12%/13% for 10s. This effect can trigger once every 20s.
